- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper deals with developing a model to recognize human actions. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is relevant as the paper deals with analyzing videos. 
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is less likely but still possible as the paper compares machine performance to human consistency on the tasks.
